quran[10]{c,v,t}:
  6,21,And who is more wrong than someone who makes up a lie (and attributes it) to God or denies His signs. Indeed the wrongdoers do not succeed
  6,22,"On a day that We gather them all together, then We say to those who associated (partners with Us): where are your partners, those you used to claim"
  6,23,"Then there would be no excuse for them except saying: by God our Master, we were not polytheist"
  6,24,"See how they lied to themselves, and what they used to make up abandoned them"
  6,25,"And some of them (pretend to) listen to you, but We placed a cover on their hearts so they do not understand it and made their ears hard of hearing, and if they see every sign they do not believe in it, until when they come to you and they argue with you. Those who disbelieved say: This (Quran) is nothing but stories of the earlier ones"
  6,26,"And they prohibit (others) from it and they keep away from it, and they only destroy themselves and they do not realize"
  6,27,"And if you see when they are made to stop by the fire, then they said: we wish we are sent back and we would not deny our Master's signs and we would become of the believers"
  6,28,"No, but what they used to hide in the past became apparent to them, and if they are sent back, they would go back to what they were forbidden from it, and indeed they are liars"
  6,29,"And they said: there is nothing but our worldly life and we will not be raised"
  6,30,"And if you see when they are made to stop before their Master, He says: is not this the truth? They say: yes, by our Master. He says: so taste the punishment because of what you used to disbelieve"